Global Oxygen Plasma Degumming Machine Market Insights
Oxygen Plasma Degumming Machine Market size was valued at USD 0.35 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.75 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.10% from 2024 to 2030.

Oxygen Plasma Degumming Machine Market Overview
The global oxygen plasma degumming machine market is expected to witness substantial growth, driven by increasing demand for high-quality fabric processing technologies across various industries. This market was valued at approximately USD 85 million in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 135 million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7% during the forecast period. The rising trend of sustainable and eco-friendly textile treatments is one of the key factors contributing to this market's growth. Additionally, the application of oxygen plasma degumming machines in the textile, automotive, and medical industries is further driving market expansion. As the demand for advanced cleaning and treatment techniques increases, the need for highly efficient and cost-effective solutions in industries like textiles is expected to push the market forward.

